divs: Sighting DetailsI just finished eating cereal and was about to wash out my bowl when I looked out my kitchen window and saw something in the sky moving from west to east, it was kind of acorn shaped with a lighter colored band close to the middle,maybe a little closer to the bottom(just off middle).The trees obstructed my view after about two seconds.I didn't know what it was so I went outside in hopes of getting a better view of it but the trees were in the way.I am not saying that this was a ufo I was just wondering if anyone else got a better look and knew what it was.
